set_short

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_short -  This method sets the short for the door.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_short(string words)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^words%^RESET%^ - the short to set for the door object. 
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/basic/door.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the short for the door.  As well as setting the short,
it calculates the name, adjectives and plurals for the door.  
.EP

